Myrmidon looked at the signature masking device idly for a moment, as
one might look at some really old out of date clothing he was being
forced to wear. With a slight growl he attatches it and climbed into
position. "Ready!" 

He grunts to himself. "All this subterfuge for one robot. This had
better be worth it!"

Preston
(Myrmidon)
